<tbody>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="50%"><strong>Best European Game</strong><br /> Battlefield : Bad Company 2 <br /><br /> <strong>Special Achievement</strong><br /> One Big Game <br /><br /> <strong>Personality Award</strong><br /> Frank Sliwka <br /><br /> <strong>Most Wanted Game</strong><br /> Crysis 2 <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Gamedesign</strong><br /> Battlefield : Bad Company 2 <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Gameworld</strong><br /> S.T.A.L.K.E.R. Call of Pripyat <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Art Direction</strong><br /> Machinarium <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Soundtrack</strong><br /> Silent Hill: Shattered Memories <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Action Game</strong><br /> Battlefield : Bad Company 2 <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Racing Game</strong><br /> Need For Speed: Shift <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Adventure</strong><br /> Heavy Rain</td>
<td valign="top" width="50%"><strong>Best European Strategy Game</strong><br /> Anno 1404 <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Handheld Game</strong><br /> LittleBigPlanet PSP <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Gaming Magazine</strong><br /> ComputerAndVideoGames <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Gaming Portal</strong><br /> Bigpoint <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Studio</strong><br /> Crytek <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Publisher</strong><br /> Ubisoft <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Online Game</strong><br /> EVE Online: Tyrannis <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Social Game</strong><br /> Bubble Island <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Browser Game</strong><br /> Farmerama <br /><br /> <strong>Best European OVI Game</strong><br /> Sonic Unleashed <br /><br /> <strong>Best European App Store Game</strong><br /> Angry Birds <br /><br /> <strong>Best European Windows Phone Game</strong><br /> Texas HoldEm Poker</td>
